    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u><strong>Work in progress: visuals and content on this page will change before release.</strong></u></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drill deeper. Get richer. Survive the depths. Come out the other side.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE LONG WAY DOWN is a first person digging game where you carve your own tunnels in real time. You mine valuable minerals, sell what you extract, and upgrade. You drill for oil, refine it into fuel, and keep pushing deeper. Demons live below and they will try to stop you. Along the way you uncover rare one off finds like fossils and buried treasures.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CORE GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig anywhere: carve tunnels and chambers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine and sell: extract valuable minerals and sell them to earn money for upgrades.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drill for oil and refine fuel: drill into oil pockets and refine it into fuel to keep your operation running.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique items: find rare one off collectibles such as fossils, treasures, and other unusual artifacts hidden in the ground.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your rig: improve drilling, speed, efficiency and others so you can reach deeper.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to keep going: the deeper you go, the more demons and other threats you will face.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GOAL</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the mission by drilling all the way through the Earth and come out the other side in China.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316220/extras/f75c036d1eeeb8bed2862ad57bffcf11.poster.avif?t=1770656760\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_